### Description

I got exclusivity violation when tried to add `@inlinable` to non-frozen structure with library evolution mode enabled.

### Reproduction

```swift
public struct Payload: ~Copyable {}

public struct Backing {
    @usableFromInline mutating func update(into payload: inout Payload) {}
}

// @frozen - works with frozen
public struct View: ~Copyable {
    @usableFromInline var backing: Backing
    @usableFromInline var payload: Payload

    @inlinable public mutating func doWork() {
        backing.update(into: &self.payload)
    }
}
```


